title: igus launches new RBTX online shopping experience for robotics developers
description:
This shift to a self-serve model removes the requirement for a sales consultation, providing a streamlined experience, igus said.

The post igus launches new RBTX online shopping experience for robotics developers appeared first on The Robot Report.
